methods.name: StateMachine_GetGlobalWeight
methods.doc: Returns the weight of a state, relative to the graph (specified in the provided FCachedAnimStateData)

methods.name: StateMachine_GetLocalWeight
methods.doc: Returns the weight of a state, relative to its state machine (specified in the provided FCachedAnimStateData)

methods.name: StateMachine_IsStateRelevant
methods.doc: Returns whether a state is relevant (specified in the provided FCachedAnimStateData)
